0000350 65535 f\r\n0000000351 65535 f\r\n0000000352 65535 f\r\n0000000353 65535 f\r\n0000000354 65535 f\r\n0000000355 65535 f\r\n0000000356 65535 f\r\n0000000357 65535 f\r\n0000000358 65535 f\r\n0000000359 65535 f\r\n0000000360 65535 f\r\n0000000361 65535 f\r\n0000000362 65535 f\r\n0000000363 65535 f\r\n0000000364 65535 f\r\n0000000365 65535 f\r\n0000000000 65535 f\r\n0000029048 00000 n\r\n0000029385 00000 n\r\n0000029729 00000 n\r\n0000029757 00000 n\r\n0000029785 00000 n\r\n0000030227 00000 n\r\n0000097672 00000 n\r\n0000098044 00000 n\r\n0000098446 00000 n\r\n0000147479 00000 n\r\n0000147685 00000 n\r\n0000147987 00000 n\r\n0000159980 00000 n\r\n0000160034 00000 n\r\n0000160335 00000 n\r\n0000171402 00000 n\r\n0000171455 00000 n\r\n0000171699 00000 n\r\ntrailer\r\n<</Size 384/Root 1 0 R/Info 47 0 R/ID[<9291C9BD3CC40E48841149F554563218><9291C9BD3CC40E48841149F554563218>] >>\r\nstartxref\r\n172722\r\n%%EOF\r\nxref\r\n0 0\r\ntrailer\r\n<</Size 384/Root 1 0 R/Info 47 0 R/ID[<9291C9BD3CC40E48841149F554563218><9291C9BD3CC40E48841149F554563218>] /Prev 172722/XRefStm 171699>>\r\nstartxref\r\n180562\r\n%%EOF', '(1).pdf', 'pdf', '236927'), (10005, 'manmathanm@imail.com', 'manmathanm52@imail.com', 'hi', 'Hello there,\r\n\r\nLet?s be honest for a moment.\r\n\r\nRight now, there are two types of students:\r\n\r\nThose who are moving ahead with clarity?\r\nAnd those who are stuck, hoping things will somehow work out.\r\n\r\nThe question is ? which one are you becoming?\r\n\r\nIf you?re experiencing this:\r\n\r\n? Studying regularly but not seeing real improvement\r\n? Forgetting what you learn after a few days\r\n? Feeling unsure about your career direction\r\n? Watching others move ahead while you feel stuck\r\n\r\nThen this is not just a phase.\r\nIt?s a pattern ? and patterns don?t change unless you break them.\r\n\r\nEvery day you wait, the gap keeps increasing.\r\n\r\nHere?s where things can change.\r\n\r\nAt Edutantr, the focus is not just on learning more ?\r\nbut on helping you learn the right way with clarity and direction.\r\n\r\nWe help you:\r\n\r\n? Understand concepts in a way that actually stays with you\r\n? Apply what you learn to real-life situations\r\n? Identify your strengths and choose the right path forward\r\n? Build confidence through structured, step-by-step progress\r\n? Stop feeling lost and start seeing real growth\r\n\r\nThis is why students who take action here don?t just study ?\r\nthey start moving forward with purpose.\r\n\r\nNow the choice is simple:\r\nStay in the same cycle? or break it.\r\n\r\n&#128073; Take Your First Step Now: https://forms.gle/UcHF2tmSTyS7h3cn6\r\n\r\n&#9889; ?A small step today can change your entire direction.?\r\n\r\nDon?t wait until it feels too late.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nAyesha\r\nEdutantr - Bangalore\r\nemail: ayesha@edutantr.in\r\nPh : +91 7975001549', '7-4-2026', '10:39:22 AM', 'spam', '%PDF-1.7\n%âãÏÓ\n4 0 obj\n<<\n/Type /XObject\n/Subtype /Image\n/Width 706\n/Height 991\n/BitsPerComponent 8\n/ColorSpace /DeviceRGB\n/Filter [/FlateDecode /DCTDecode]\n/DecodeParms [null <<\n/Quality 60\n>>]\n/Length 70342\n>>\nstream\nxœìýeX]]³6\nNX¸»[`áÜ58
